$ON_CMT5
Onevent BEFORE_AREA Gosub AV_CMT5 From W1PJMBUD0
Return

$AV_CMT5
## Action INIDEV
GDEVFMT="11.2" : GDEVFMT = GDEVFMT1(max(find([M:PJBU0]CMT4(nolign-1),GDEVISE(1..GNBDEV)),1))
Chgfmt [M]CMT5(indice) With "NPz3:"+GDEVFMT
Gosub _AFF
Return

